lass=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3218160/extras/318c9bc9546364f1370c10b1e1bdb95a.avif?t=1773961960\" width=435 height=92 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In an age where dragons rule the sky, humanity has fallen to its knees. <br>Kingdoms either bow before their flames—or burn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>You awaken in another world as one of the legendary Dragon Riders—able to command dragons themselves, and build your own dragon harem. <br>As a Dragon Rider, when you claim a dragon—when you ride her—you bind her will and power to your own. <br><br>Can you defy mankind’s fate as prey and rise above gods and dragons alike? The world awaits your domination, Dragon Master!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3218160/extras/829f9852d27cc346cf7105a0aae27baa.avif?t=1773961960\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3218160/extras/fab98079ca0dafb4ef70890c6c7e49b8.avif?t=1773961960\" width=435 height=92 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A fast-paced roguelite drenched in Japanese flair. Face swarms of enemies and mighty bosses, gather rewards, and grow stronger with every battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3218160/extras/2570d85d23179d96c9fa05b56b6c3b99.poster.avif?